data.description: Welcome to 18329 Willow Sage Ln, Elgin, TX 78621—a slice of tranquility just for you! This charming home 5 bedroom home PLUS AN OFFICE offers a spacious interior, perfect for comfortable living. The well-equipped kitchen is a delight for any chef with a flow that makes sense and a large peninsula counter-top island. With a serene backyard, this is your personal oasis to unwind in at the end of your day. Embrace the Elgin lifestyle while savoring modern comforts. The home has been well taken care of and passes along a new roof laid in 2021, new water heater in 2022, a water softener AND a reverse osmosis system. And it that is not enough, the home has solar panels which will convey. Your new journey begins at Willow Sage Ln—visit today and make it yours!
